ğŸ“¡ API Endpoint

POST /chat

Sends a user question and receives an AI-generated response.

Request:

{
  "question": "What is mparticle?"
}

Response:

{
  "answer": "Check mParticle docs here: https://docs.mparticle.com/."
}


